#
# Base run: all active operators set to 0.9999... (effectively C=1)
#
# This card generates 406 reweight points:
#   1      SM           (all C = 0)
#   27     single +1    (one C = +1, rest = 0)
#   27     single -1    (one C = -1, rest = 0)
#   351    pairs        (two C = +1, rest = 0)
#
# Operators read from: /Users/albertodufour/code/DY2026/analysis/restriction_card/operator_scan.html
#
# CP-odd operators (SMEFTcpv block) are untouched throughout.
#
#*************************************************************************

